ss with website pages, business blogging, video and podcast hosting, smart content, landing pages and forms, SEO recommendations, forms and lead flow, web analytics reporting, calls-to-action, and file manager. It offers Operations Hub, which provides programmable automation, data sync, data curation, and data quality tools; and Commerce Hub, a B2B commerce suite that provides payment links, invoices, quotes, subscription management, and automation and revenue reporting; and breeze, an AI that powers the customer platform that provides AI-powered insights, automation, content generation, and data enrichment, as well as Breeze Assistant, a go-to-market assistant to boost productivity and make work easier; and Breeze Agents, which helps teams automate work end-to-end from strategy to execution. In addition, the company provides professional services to educate and train customers on how to utilize its CRM platform; and customer success; phone and/or email and chat-based support services; and helps customers by providing Customer Success Manager and Partner Development Manager digital channels through educational content academey. It serves mid-market business-to-business companies. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Cambridge, Massachusetts.","industry":"Software - Application","sector":"Technology","marketCap":10178248704,"trailingPE":104.09948,"forwardPE":12.734241,"pegRatio":0.32,"priceToBook":5.1732845,"priceToSales":3.0860722,"profitMargin":3.04,"operatingMargin":3.2960000000000003,"grossMargin":83.655,"returnOnEquity":5.011,"returnOnAssets":1.0980001,"revenueGrowthYoy":23.400000000000002,"earningsGrowthYoy":null,"earningsQuarterlyGrowthYoy":null,"debtToEquity":12.384,"currentRatio":1.609,"quickRatio":1.348,"freeCashFlow":656183360,"operatingCashFlow":797971968,"totalCash":1691052032,"totalDebt":247291008,"revenue":3298124032,"dividendYield":null,"payoutRatio":0,"beta":1.229,"fiftyTwoWeekHigh":621.16,"fiftyTwoWeekLow":173.25,"targetMeanP